    <title>Amending the Rules of the House of Representatives to require the Committee on Appropriations to maintain proposed and historical budget authority and outlays for each category of spending.</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <actionDate>2016-04-21</actionDate>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <updateDate>2016-04-21T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-05-05T16:18:24Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Declares that the Committee on Appropriations shall maintain proposed and historical budget authority and outlays for each category of spending. </p> <p>Specifies that such data shall: </p> <ul> <li>cover a period comprising the 10 fiscal years immediately preceding the budget year, and</li> <li>be kept up-to-date and provided on the Committee's website. </li> </ul>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
